{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"10a899d8f8","title":"两案内不属中央管理的干部已判刑和拟判刑人员登记表 -- 崔建雄","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8b5dd98674","index":0,"year":1979,"month":10,"day":21,"articleId":"10a899d8f8","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"293d4ae892","name":"中共内蒙党委运动办公室"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[{"id":"5e9beca6d4","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{},"index":-1,"part_index":-1,"offset":-1,"text":"来源：根据中央文件翻印件打印"}],"contents":[{"id":"3880f8ea92","type":"title","text":"两案内不属中央管理的干部已判刑和拟判刑人员登记表 -- 崔建雄","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f0c4679ee5","type":"paragraph","text":"崔建雄，男，39岁，行政22级，贫农出身，学生成份，陕西省绥德县人，汉族，1975年2月入党，1959年入伍，文化革命前是黄管局任会计。文化革命中任巴盟革委会副主任、内蒙革委会委员。现在系黄管局器材财务科副科长。","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"672498b8af","type":"paragraph","text":"主要罪行","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3d2170184d","type":"paragraph","text":"一、大搞刑讯逼供，是制造巴盟地区“新内人党”冤、假、错案的操纵者和指挥者之一。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"813e3e10cd","type":"paragraph","text":"1968年“挖肃”挖“新内人党”期间，崔建雄亲自主持召开盟革委会第111次、113次、124次常委会议，研究了巴图巴根等120余位同志的所谓问题。给这些同志无辜扣上“内人党”、“叛徒”、“特务”、“死不改悔的走资派”等罪名，决定群专和打倒。崔说：“这些人本质上是坏的，打开骨头也是黑的”。为了突破巴盟所谓“新内人党”，崔利用分管专案办公室的权力，亲自指使专案人员和原盟委公署的审讯小组成员昼夜进行突击审讯、严刑逼供。崔给帮兄弟鼓劲说：“内人党证据确凿，我摸到一个规律，‘内人党’不打不说，一打就说”，“‘内人党’是反革命组织，要狠狠的审讯、狠狠的打。”致使白瑞卿等同志被逼含冤而死。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"36cca77faf","type":"paragraph","text":"二、分裂群众队伍，并抢夺武器，私造武器，挑起武斗事件。给巴盟地区的革命和生产造成严重损失。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1c662548b7","type":"paragraph","text":"1968年1月黄河一处的部分工人与革委会几名工作人员由于误会而发生冲突，崔建雄等故意扩大事态，说是反革命事件，煽动近千名工人围剿一处，当时盟革委责成崔建雄出面调停处理，崔不但不制止，反而挑起武斗。有三、四十人被打，这就是当时的“血流黄河一处”事件。1969年5月崔又亲自指挥策划一场大型武斗，把拖拉机改制成土坦克，从磴口五原煽动农民参加武斗。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f5795b3ee7","type":"paragraph","text":"崔建雄6月20日从呼市到五原参加三干会，亲自跑到五原胜丰、和胜两公社人武部要枪20支。公社不同意，崔便将盟革委人保组手枪3支和专案组79子弹150余发、762子弹70多发和小口径步枪子弹交给“东联”头头苏振清和磴口的熊占海、石玉喜等人。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"23a4745f64","type":"paragraph","text":"崔在五原期间一面同五原工代会赵文秉、候在高研究制做了一部分土制手榴弹，一面派李玉清到临河干召庙、五星两公社了解枪支、子弹。于6月20日由王建国带20余人把干召庙公社武装部枪36支、子弹20发抢回。6月29日崔派人带武器到磴口黄土垱公社集结。结果被打散，伤几十人。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4bf488e4eb","type":"paragraph","text":"三、利用群专残酷迫害干部群众。1968年1月24日崔支持原“巴盟群专指挥部”搞所谓统一行动，借机进行派性专政。搜查不同观点的干部和群众的家，抓了原巴镇工筹会负责人李仁同志等送公检法拘留数月。将一中学生门龙生、史德平搜家之后又拘留审讯一周。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ce35a03411","type":"paragraph","text":"四、拉帮结派，阴谋篡党夺权。内蒙六次全委会期间，崔伙同郝广德、王金保等人干扰会议正常进行，向内蒙党委施加压力，要内蒙党委在全国四届人大代表中增加造反派代表名额，崔签名联名向中央政治局发电报。崔回临河后，抢占盟招待所33号房间，垒起“33”号山头，冲击盟委会议，围攻盟委领导，召开黑会，散布黑指示，张贴大幅标语，“要通过批林批孔运动解决造反派受压局面，把失掉的权力夺回来。”再次搞乱巴盟。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"24bd46e100","type":"paragraph","text":"问题性质：反革命罪","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6701960840","type":"paragraph","text":"认罪态度：","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f000dc367f","type":"paragraph","text":"在党的政策感召下有所交待，认罪态度不好。","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a8d294ab1b","type":"paragraph","text":"处刑意见：","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f29e6382a0","type":"paragraph","text":"起诉、判刑。","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"20073c3a9a","type":"paragraph","text":"两案内不属中央管理的干部已判刑和拟判刑人员登记表","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"250fd9074c","type":"paragraph","text":"审查单位：　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　案别：","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"73fa73424a","type":"paragraph","text":"————","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"96ccad42ff","type":"paragraph","text":"姓名  崔建雄 | 性别  男 | 年龄  39 | 级别  22","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c6aa62fc7e","type":"paragraph","text":"————","index":20,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cd09c4913e","type":"paragraph","text":"家庭出身 贫农|本人成份 学生|籍贯 陕西省绥德县|民族 汉","index":21,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9d32bc8b89","type":"paragraph","text":"————","index":22,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7779596486","type":"paragraph","text":"入党时间","index":23,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7a0f39774b","type":"paragraph","text":"1975.2","index":24,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8e755cba9f","type":"paragraph","text":"——","index":25,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1469225165","type":"paragraph","text":"入伍时间","index":26,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0591fbe349","type":"paragraph","text":"1951","index":27,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e93c956f53","type":"paragraph","text":"|","index":28,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"11251e5013","type":"paragraph","text":"|职务|","index":29,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d5d28a1b11","type":"paragraph","text":"文化革命前","index":30,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c02341d866","type":"paragraph","text":"黄管局任会计","index":31,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f754c1e98c","type":"paragraph","text":"——","index":32,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b80c4555e4","type":"paragraph","text":"文化革命中","index":33,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e2effc9598","type":"paragraph","text":"巴盟革委会副主任、内蒙革委会委员","index":34,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c5acb75e3a","type":"paragraph","text":"——","index":35,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"92aeffbabb","type":"paragraph","text":"现在","index":36,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6c6459294c","type":"paragraph","text":"黄管局器材财务科副科长","index":37,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5c9a187558","type":"paragraph","text":"————","index":38,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7612715c83","type":"paragraph","text":"主要罪行","index":39,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"80ce107d26","type":"paragraph","text":"一、大搞刑讯逼供，是制造巴盟地区“新内人党”冤、错、假案的操纵者和指挥者之一。1968年“挖肃”、挖“新内人党”期间，崔建雄亲自主持召开盟革委会第111次、113次、124次常委会议，专门研究了巴图巴根等120余位同志的所谓问题，给这些同志无辜扣上“内人党”、“叛徒”、“特务”、“死不改悔的走资派”等罪名，决定群专和打倒，崔在会上公然胡说：“这些人本质是坏的，打开骨头也是黑的”。1968年10月下旬，为了突破巴盟所谓“新内人党”，崔利用分管专案办公室的权力，亲自指使专案人员和原盟委公署的审讯小组成员，对巴图巴根等同志，昼夜进行突击审讯、严刑逼供。崔给帮兄弟鼓劲，打气说：“内人党证据确凿，我摸到一个规律，‘内人党’不打不说，一打就说，内人党是反革命组织，要狠狠的审讯，狠狠的打，除了头部以外，打坏了我负责。”致使白瑞卿等同志被逼而含冤死去。","index":40,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"40891e6962","type":"paragraph","text":"二、分裂群众队伍，挑起武斗事件。给巴盟地区的革命和生产造成严重损失。1968年1月黄河一处的部分工人与革委会几名工作人员由于误会而发生冲突，崔建雄派“东联”的几个头头，故意扩大事态，说是反革命事件，发表声明，煽动近千名工人围剿一处，当时盟革委责成崔建雄出面调停处理，崔不但不制止“东联”的错误作法，挑起武斗，有三、四十人被打，这就是当时的“血流黄河一处”事件。1969年5月，“东联”策划一场大型武斗，从磴口、五原，煽动农民上访，围攻另一派总部，用土制坦克将垟推倒，崔打电话说：“既围就拿下来。”","index":41,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"642010b641","type":"paragraph","text":"三、私制土手榴弹，抢夺武器。崔建雄6月20日从呼市到五原参加三干会，亲自跑到五原胜丰、和胜两公社人武部要枪20支，公社不同意。崔便将盟革委人保组手枪3支和专案组79子弹150余发、762子弹70余发和小口径步枪子弹交给“东联”头头苏振清和磴口的熊占海、石玉喜等人。","index":42,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"30edc4d160","type":"paragraph","text":"崔在五原期间，一面同五原工代会赵文秉、候在高研究制做了一部分土制手榴弹，一面派李玉清到临河干召庙、五星两公社了解枪支、子弹。于6月20日由王建国带20余人把干召庙公社武装部枪36支、子弹20发抢回。6月29日崔的一派人带武器到磴口黄土垱集结，“黄土垱之战”双方伤几十人。","index":43,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d28ab84d4c","type":"paragraph","text":"四、利用群专打击不同观点的群众。1968年1月24日崔支持原“巴盟群专指挥部”搞所谓统一行动，借机进行派性专政。搜查不同观点的干部和群众的家，抓了原巴镇工筹会负责人李仁同志，并送公检法拘留数月。并将一中学生门龙生、史德平搜家之后又拘留审讯一周。","index":44,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"46f93a6970","type":"paragraph","text":"五、拉帮结派，阴谋篡党夺权。内蒙六次全委会期间，崔伙同郝广德、王金保等人，干扰会议正常进行，向内蒙党委施加压力，要内蒙党委在全国四届人大代表中增加造反派代表名额，崔签名联名向中央政治局发电报。崔回临河后，抢占盟招待所33号房间，垒起33号山头，再次搞乱巴盟地区形势，并以此为据点，召开黑会，传播黑指示，张贴大幅标语，声称“要通过批林批孔运动解决造反派受压局面，把失掉的权力夺回来。”","index":45,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cb922f933f","type":"paragraph","text":"六、冲击盟委会议，围攻盟委领导。1973年10月，在崔的带领下，冲击盟常委会议，对开会的常委进行围攻，无理纠缠，迫使会议中断，并带人冲击旗县委书记会议，召开413大会，发表反盟委讲话，出动宣传车向盟委示威。","index":46,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"020bdf0e62","type":"paragraph","text":"————","index":47,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f1479ee364","type":"paragraph","text":"问题性质    反革命罪","index":48,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0a5ae7110b","type":"paragraph","text":"————","index":49,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e521664e28","type":"paragraph","text":"认罪态度    在党的政策感召下，有所交待，认罪态度不好","index":50,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7669bf2df4","type":"paragraph","text":"————","index":51,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4d69a9d884","type":"paragraph","text":"处刑意见    起诉、判刑","index":52,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"297ed5899f","type":"paragraph","text":"————","index":53,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"90fca7df8d","type":"paragraph","text":"备注","index":54,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0467bdbfff","type":"paragraph","text":"————","index":55,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2e09f6b9ac","type":"paragraph","text":" \t79年10月21日填","index":56,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c9aa51164c","type":"paragraph","text":"来源：根据中央文件翻印件打印","index":57,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"10a899d8f8","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}